import styled from "styled-components"
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar"
import Games from "../components/Games"

const Container = styled.div`

`

const Title = styled.h1`
    margin: 20px;
`

const GameList = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
        <Navbar />
        <Title>Games</Title>
        <GameList />
    </Container>
  )
}

export default GameList
